<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240621/1718944019126014110.jpg" title="1718944019126014110.jpg" alt="6727ed5801676c39347463acd574ab19.jpg" style="width: 887px; height: 2073px;" width="887" height="2073"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(75, 75, 75); line-height: 1.6em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">阳光透过树叶洒下斑驳的光影<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(75, 75, 75); line-height: 1.6em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">每一片绿叶都在低语：</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(75, 75, 75); line-height: 1.6em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">夏天来了</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(75, 75, 75); line-height: 1.6em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">草地音乐节已提上日程</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(75, 75, 75); line-height: 1.6em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">献给那些曾在春天许下愿望的同学们</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(75, 75, 75); line-height: 1.6em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">让我们在栀子花开的毕业季</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(75, 75, 75); line-height: 1.6em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">共赴一场</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(75, 75, 75); line-height: 1.6em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">音乐、草地、星空、晚风</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(75, 75, 75); line-height: 1.6em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">岁月、成长、热情、浪漫</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.6em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">夏夜星声之约</span></p><p style="text-align: center; text-indent: 0em;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240621/1718944051021088231.jpg" title="1718944051021088231.jpg" alt="1d9f0a1ca3c0c7de240d086afc5f3f59.jpg" style="width: 887px; height: 2508px;" width="887" height="2508"/></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: left;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 31.875px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">随着大学生活的结束，每年的毕业季都是学生们充满感慨和不舍的时刻。为了给学生们提供一个难忘的毕业回忆，并庆祝他们即将踏入新的人生阶段，我们策划了一场名为</span>“潮热之夜，嗨爆江软”<span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 31.875px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">为主题的大学生毕业季音乐节。</span></span></p><p style="text-align: left; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 31.875px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">毕业季音乐节，点燃青春激情！大家欢聚一堂，用音符串联回忆，用歌声释放情感。这不仅是音乐的盛宴，更是情感的狂欢。让大家共同庆祝成长，留下难忘的毕业印记，用音乐传递对未来的无限憧憬与希望！</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">2024年6月21日17:30<br/>A12音乐广场<br/>&nbsp;标记你的日历吧！<br/>这个傍晚，可不要缺席哦！<br/>让我们在这个夏天<br/>以音乐的名义<br/>共赴一场关于生命、激情<br/>与梦想的约会<br/>不见不散<br/>让“潮热之夜，嗨爆江软”<br/>成为你记忆中<br/>最闪耀的篇章！</span></p>